@startuml
participant "GitHub Repository" as GitHub
participant "GitHub Actions" as GHA
participant "AWS ECS" as ECS
participant "Appian" as Appian
participant "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "BigMAC" as BigMAC
participant "AWS SNS" as SNS
participant "AWS CloudWatch" as CloudWatch

GitHub -> GHA : Trigger deployment
GHA -> ECS : Deploy Kafka Connector
ECS -> Appian : Extract data changes
Appian --> ECS : Return data changes
ECS -> Kafka : Stream data changes
Kafka -> BigMAC : Forward data changes
ECS -> CloudWatch : Log events
CloudWatch -> SNS : Trigger alerts (if needed)
SNS -> GitHub : Notify developers
@enduml